snippet.title: PKA 568 w/Filthy Robot - Jail Souvenirs, Twitch Leaks, Dune
snippet.description:

0:00:00 - Woody introduces the show and guest, Taylor introduces sponsors
0:00:12 - Filthy’s hand injury, streamers who grind one game & backseat gamers
0:08:05 - Why reddit sucks nowadays, censored adult subreddits & niche hobbies 
0:16:06 - Woody’s glitch in the Matrix experience, /r/Retcon and the Mandela Effect 
0:23:33 - PKA tests their false memories of logos and experiences the Mandela effect
0:32:26 - PKA’s Cool Guy of The Week: Man swaps wife’s rowdy cat for a trained one 
0:40:33 - The time Taylor’s dogs accidentally ate cat food and it got MESSY
0:44:06 - Kyle’s dog with no eyes and bowel problems & how to make a kangaroo cat
0:47:43 - Cops who put down dogs & the tragic story of Daniel Shaver’s demise 
0:52:06 - Kyle & Woody place a wager on the trial outcome of the 2020 Kenosha incident  
1:04:19 - PKA attempts to make a coffee brand for left-leaning liberals 
1:07:43 - Movie talk: Woody, Taylor and Filthy review Dune (2021) [spoiler alert]
1:25:04 - The dismal world of corporate office jobs & why the guys would never go back
1:27:48 - Corporate America and Hollywood's insane mistreatment of child labour
1:33:22 - Why do younger generations despise the concept of landlords? 
1:34:44 - Is getting a college degree a waste of time in 2021? Taylor and Woody discuss 
1:38:42 - Kyle’s plans to acquire a fake business degree & get hired by Chipotle
1:43:59 - Here’s how PKA is going to get Lock and Load on store shelves nationwide! 
1:50:58 - Ad reads: Feals & Lucy
1:53:53 - Get 10% off your PKA Lock and Load shipment before stocks run out!
1:59:39 - Kyle’s impromptu Illinois vacation & why the State’s legal weed sucks 
2:03:56 - Florida’s medical weed availability & the time Kyle bought a boat in Florida 
2:08:44 - UFC 268 talk: Usman vs Covington 2, Thug Rose vs Weili Zhang 2 & more
2:23:13 - Kyle & Taylor’s fantasy plan get together and live in Nelly’s old mansion 
2:28:08 - The bodybuilder with an absurd off-season physique (Jay Cutler)
2:34:51 - Pumping Iron - Arnold Schwarzeneggar’s fascinating 1977 documentary
2:40:23 - More on Kyle’s Illinois trip & the guys discuss doing an in-person PKA 
2:48:12 - Taylor’s hyperactive dog and his recent garage/home gym improvements 
2:52:40 - Why being a goalkeeper in ice hockey absolutely SUCKS 
2:58:54 - Filthy’s venture into soccer & Woody’s friend with a NASTY ankle sprain
3:04:56 - PKA reacts to Twitch’s huge leak of streamer earnings & source coding
3:12:52 - Taylor explains why he stopped streaming due to his wife’s medical emergency 
3:21:09 - Fitness talk: Woody’s new EZ curl bar & Kyle’s plans to build a home gym
3:34:23 - Filthy’s rock climbing hobby & Woody’s friend with a $50,000 bike 
3:39:05 - How lockdown and mask mandates are affecting the guys’ hobbies
3:43:05 - Kyle explains how he would become Lord of the remote North Sentinel Island 
3:49:16 - Conquistadores, native Americans & are horses native to America? 
4:01:35 - Woody’s positive review Netflix’s latest series “You” 
4:03:25 - Which serious crime would Filthy’s loved ones have to commit for him to snitch?
4:07:17 - Kyle reflect’s on Drift0r’s recent guest appearance and his wild stories
4:09:36 - Kyle is absolutely terrified of seeing shadowy figures in the middle of the night
4:12:25 - Filthy shouts out his social medias, Woody calls it a show
